{"tid":606563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"子華呼籲大家唔好買黃牛","createTime":"2018-03-26T14:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T07:08:26.000Z","uid":39394,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"94c2971ada5057188607999b75111f79d3a004fd","tid":606563,"uid":39394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:42:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dayowongoffical/posts/1276938469105689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdayowongoffical%2Fposts%2F1276938469105689&d=77LTAM%2BkkH8ks%2FmAMaxNoBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=dbe7105f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dayowongoffical/posts/1276938469105689</a><br />\n<br />\n各位今日買唔到飛嘅巴絲<br />\n唔使擔心 亦唔使咁急高價買黃牛住<br />\n子華話之後會有好多飛買<br />\n而且每人限買4張<br />\n雖然無可避免仲會有好多黃牛搶晒啲飛<br />\n但希望各位忍一忍<br />\n就算最後買唔到都唔好買黃牛<br />\n今日你比幾千佢賺<br />\n下次全香港又要搶唔到飛 同捱貴飛<br />\n只要全香港齊心啲 堅決唔買黃牛<br />\n等佢地蝕到仆街<br />\n以後我地先有好日子過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記住呢班人今日害到你浪費幾個鐘<br />\n害到你買唔到飛<br />\n你唔係諗住比錢佢地賺呀嘛"},{"pid":"f03095290155f1619ed200348c1c14f302016d2d","tid":606563,"uid":39394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:45:25.000Z","msg":"大家千其唔好益炒飛狗<br />\n大家都唔買<br />\n到時可能會低過原價求你接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0d8bf6f7f222b2f23e5ae57ba13471deaeb04b","tid":606563,"uid":58071,"like":0,"dislike":29,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:47:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30dc6e833fdf1981a9145e6bf9623ca808b2da15","tid":606563,"uid":39394,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"呢個係革命<br />\n大家要堅持 誓死唔買黃牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff35d355ddadfd3e921e0cf3e105fc44a4288d82","tid":606563,"uid":65587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"神即係神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ad